es across Uganda in clean water, education, health, livelihoods, leadership, and community transformation.</p></div><div class="col-lg-6"><img src="/pictures/unnamed (27).webp" class="rounded-4 shadow w-100" alt="Kyagulanyi Ministries community gathering"></div></div></div></section><section class="impact-section"><div class="container text-center"><p class="eyebrow text-warning">Our impact</p><h2 class="text-white">Lives changed. Communities transformed.</h2><div class="row mt-4">@foreach([['12,540+','Lives impacted'],['46','Churches planted'],['38','Water projects'],['2,300+','Children supported'],['120+','Communities reached'],['6','Districts reached']] as [$value,$label])<div class="col-6 col-md-2"><strong class="metric-value d-block">{{$value}}</strong><small>{{$label}}</small></div>@endforeach</div></div></section><section class="section-padding"><div class="container"><div class="text-center"><p class="eyebrow">Our leadership</p><h2>Meet our leadership</h2></div><div class="row g-4 mt-3">@foreach([['Pastor John Kyagulanyi','Founder & Senior Pastor'],['Grace Namukasa','Executive Director'],['Samuel Kato','Programs Director'],['Esther Nalwadda','Finance & Admin Manager']] as [$name,$role])<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3"><div class="card text-center p-4 h-100"><div class="avatar mx-auto mb-3">{{substr($name,0,1)}}</div><h5>{{$name}}</h5><p class="text-success fw-bold">{{$role}}</p><p class="small text-muted">Serving communities with vision, care, and accountability.</p></div></div>@endforeach</div></div></section><section class="cta-section"><div class="container text-center"><h2 class="text-white">Be Part of What God Is Doing</h2><a class="btn btn-brand btn-lg" href="/donate">Donate Now</a><a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg ms-2" href="/volunteer">Volunteer</a></div></section></body></html>
